  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6686276/" class="title-link">修齐治平 莫过于此</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6686276"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/fuyinbook/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u17856359-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/fuyinbook/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">究竟文化</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-05-29"
      class="main-meta">2014-05-29 17:24:19</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6686276_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  学习传统文化的传家宝。。。 《群书治要》是中国文化最精华的所在，世法里面最宝贵的东西，浓缩了圣贤智慧的精髓。欲修齐治平，莫过于此。也是习仲勋、马英九、净空法师、饶宗颐都曾经推荐过的好书。每个中国家庭应该家家必备一套，精读细读，代代传承。

